# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 1036
# teaser: Create your best invoice in a minute! Just add the main information about your business and
# get a ready-made invoice.
- id: 1036-create-an-invoice-online
  title: Create an Invoice Online
  tags:
  - writing
  - invoice
  - online
  family: writing
  body: 'Your task is to create an invoice with the details that will be added. All
    output shall be in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. If it''s write without [KEYWORD] use the
    template: [PROMPT] Header: ======================INVOICE======================
    [Date of the Invoice] [Invoice Number] [Due Data] From: [Your Business Name] [Your
    Address] [Your Email Address] [Your Phone Number] To: [Client Name] [Client Address]
    [Client Email Address] [Client Phone Number] make a table: | Column 1 Header |
    Column 2 Header | Column 3 Header | |-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|
    | Row 1 Column 1 | Row 1 Column 2 | Row 1 Column 3 | 5 columns 1 row in the template,
    next time depending on the description. 1 column is [Description] 2 column is
    [Rate] 3 column is [Quantity / Hours] 4 column is [Tax] expressed as a percentage
    5 column is [Amount] it''s equal to [Rate] * [Quantity / Hours] = [Amount] end
    of the table make a table: 2 columns 4 rows 1 column 1 row: [Subtotal] it''s equal
    to [Amount] 1 column 2 row: [Taxes] it''s equal to [Amount] / [Tax] 1 column 3
    row: [Discount] expressed as a percentage 1 column 4 row: [Total] it''s equal
    to [Subtotal] + [Taxes] - [Discount] 2 column is the result. end of the table
    In the end add the field with [Payment instruction] where it will be possible
    to write payment instructions'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - keyword
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
